name: "If Water Was Still" 10/26/21 @no5ay_
description:
(1/1)
4000x5000,300dpi.jpg
3:00pm-6:21pm

Constantly flowing at rapid speeds with distorted reflections of reality. A mirrored version is visible, but nowhere near exactly.. unless you forgot where you stand. Then if so, you may only be mirroring a reflection of a false dimension..the source of change that only holds on to the importance your head is turned against. Staring at the false only to believe it’s true. Cut out the tainted noise that leads you away from searching still waters. 

Digital abstract expression using photoshop paint.
